revision.text:
{{DISPLAYTITLE:Plane_Align}} {{Special|181|floor, ceiling, lineid|Miscellaneous|use=line}}
{{warning|text=This special is not fully supported by the [[UDMF]] map format. Certain parameters, noted below, have been made obsolete by the ability to directly specify properties within the linedef structure. These parameters should be set to 0 when using the UDMF format.}}
* ''floor'': “1” slopes the floor on front side of the line; “2” slopes the floor on the back side. * ''ceiling'': Same as for ''floor'', but for the ceiling plane, respectively. * ''lineid'': also sets this line's id if non-zero. ''Obsolete in UDMF.''
Note: A value of 0 means no sloping is applied.
Aligns the plane of the floor and/or ceiling depending on the values ''floor'' and ''ceiling''. For a more extensive look, check out [[slopes]].
==Examples== An example WAD can be found {{plainlink|[http://zdoom.org/files/examples/slopes2.zip here]}}. {{noexamples}}
== Conversions from linedef types == The following Doom map format types can be converted as Plane_Align: {| {{prettytable}} !Type!!Conversion!!Trigger |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 340:Slope Front Floor || Plane_Align (1, 0) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 341:Slope Front Ceiling || Plane_Align (0, 1) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 342:Slope Front Floor & Ceiling || Plane_Align (1, 1) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 343:Slope Back Floor || Plane_Align (2, 0) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 344:Slope Back Ceiling || Plane_Align (0, 2) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 345:Slope Back Floor & Ceiling || Plane_Align (2, 2) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 346:Slope Back Floor & Front Ceiling || Plane_Align (2, 1) || |- |{{icon|ZDoom}} 347:Slope Front Floor & Back Ceiling || Plane_Align (1, 2) || |- |{{icon|Eternity}} 386:Slope_FrontsectorFloor || Plane_Align (1, 0) || |- |{{icon|Eternity}} 387:Slope_FrontsectorCeiling || Plane_Align (0, 1) || |- |{{icon|Eternity}} 388:Slope_FrontsectorFloorAndCeiling || Plane_Align (1, 1) || |- |{{icon|Eternity}} 389:Slope_BacksectorFloor || Plane_Align (2, 0) || |- |{{icon|Eternity}} 390:Slope_BacksectorCeiling || Plane_Align (0, 2) || |- |{{icon|Eternity}} 391:Slope_BacksectorFloorAndCeiling || Plane_Align (2, 2) || |- |{{icon|Eternity}} 392:Slope_BackFloorAndFrontCeiling || Plane_Align (2, 1) || |- |{{icon|Eternity}} 393:Slope_BackCeilingAndFrontFloor || Plane_Align (1, 2) || |}
